-- 02_revenue_by_attribution_channel.sql
WITH latest_attribution AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel,
    attributed_at,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY customer_id ORDER BY attributed_at DESC) as rn
  FROM customer_channels
),
customer_primary_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    customer_id,
    channel
  FROM latest_attribution
  WHERE rn = 1
),
transactions_with_channel AS (
  SELECT 
    t.transaction_id,
    t.customer_id,
    t.store_id,
    t.amount,
    t.transaction_date,
    COALESCE(cpc.channel, 'unattributed') as channel,
    s.city
  FROM transactions t
  LEFT JOIN customer_primary_channel cpc ON t.customer_id = cpc.customer_id
  LEFT JOIN stores s ON t.store_id = s.store_id
)
SELECT 
  channel,
  COALESCE(city, 'unknown') as city,
  SUM(amount) as total_revenue,
  COUNT(*) as transaction_count,
  COUNT(DISTINCT customer_id) as unique_customers
FROM transactions_with_channel
GROUP BY channel, COALESCE(city, 'unknown')
ORDER BY channel, city
